{"tid":1389832,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母12點喇，大交合你掛定唔撚掛8號架！人地啲野點安排呀你老味！","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:52:35.000Z","uid":12628,"like":664,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"9a5ed70c374e5070567f94dfb16d1588730dfe14","tid":1389832,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"掛就掛，唔掛就唔掛，屌你老母咩係或者掛！<br />\n人人都坐係到等比你點呀！<br />\n唔撚使安排啲野架！<br />\n一係講明幾點掛，一係咪撚掛！<br />\n依家咁想點撚樣呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8130283c80d419e587ce57673c90444155c56f54","tid":1389832,"uid":810,"like":217,"dislike":2,"score":215,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"我彈出彈入呀你咬我食呀?<br />\n彈出彈入呀打我丫笨"},{"pid":"a08d66256ffe0f0dcc7ee806d4d52a9dd9a0f8e2","tid":1389832,"uid":134012,"like":137,"dislike":6,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"咪話咗2點前會掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b102408eacff07b0e8a63f1812669ef08fca9b","tid":1389832,"uid":127708,"like":161,"dislike":3,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"咪講咗<br />\n<br />\n【八號預警】天文台會在7月31日14:00或以前發出八號熱帶氣旋警告信號，本港風勢將會加強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a938d0731c5959299e1f5de54fe39309617293a","tid":1389832,"uid":289560,"like":8,"dislike":47,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c135be4b55eaf912ec41704ae891022c10ab8d0c","tid":1389832,"uid":2613,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"盲撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5613cfe